1. The account labeled "Paid-in Capital" represents the capital contributed by shareholders in exchange for shares.

2. The initial amount for "Paid-in Capital" is 13000000.00 as of 2023-12-31.

3. The ending amount for "Paid-in Capital" is 13000000.00 as of 2024-01-28.

Since there has been no change in the Paid-in Capital between the initial and end dates, the shareholders did not contribute any additional capital during this period.
